    <innerclass refid="classStmLogger" prot="public">StmLogger</innerclass>
    <briefdescription>
<para>STM32 Logger — UART/SWO/ITM-based logging with full <ref refid="classBaseLogger" kindref="compound">BaseLogger</ref> interface. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Supports multiple output backends:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>UART (via CubeMX UART handle) — most common for STM32</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>SWO/ITM (via ITM stimulus port) — for SWD debugging</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>printf (via _write syscall / semihosting) — fallback</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<sect1 id="StmTypes_8h_1Usage">
<title>Usage</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keyword">extern</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>UART_HandleTypeDef<sp/>huart2;</highlight></codeline>
